title: Friendly Match 1
note: Get ready to sweat and have fun with us at Boston Badminton in Westborough, MA on April 5th at 9:00am. Come prepared to work on your footwork, strategy, and power. All skill levels are welcome!

title: Friendly Match 2

note: Come join our badminton community at the Bay Badminton Center in South San Francisco, CA on May 2nd at 6:00pm. Meet new people, play new opponents, and enjoy the game you love. No pressure, just fun!

title: Friendly Match 3
